{% extends "_base.html.j2" %}

{% block head_extra %}
<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--h-navy);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 56px 24px 48px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 38px);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .page-hero p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .process-step {
    padding: 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--h-gray-light);
  }
  .process-step:last-of-type { border-bottom: 0; }
  .step-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .step-badge {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--h-teal);
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .step-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--h-navy);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .step-body { padding-left: 68px; }
  .step-body p { margin-bottom: 14px; color: var(--h-dark-text); line-height: 1.65; }
  .expect-box {
    background: var(--h-gray-bg);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--h-teal);
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .expect-box h4 {
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--h-teal);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .expect-box ul { margin-left: 18px; }
  .expect-box li { font-size: 14.5px; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--h-dark-text); }

  .bottom-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 56px 24px;
    background: var(--h-gray-bg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--h-gray-light);
  }
  .bottom-cta h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--h-navy); font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .bottom-cta p { color: var(--h-gray-text); max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 24px; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .step-body { padding-left: 0; }
  }
</style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="page-hero">
  <h1>How It Works</h1>
  <p>Four steps from curiosity to clarity — use our tools, learn from the data, and make better health decisions.</p>
</section>

<div class="container">
  <nav class="breadcrumbs">
    <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> How It Works
  </nav>

  <div class="process-step">
    <div class="step-header">
      <span class="step-badge">1</span>
      <h2>Assess Where You Stand</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="step-body">
      <p>Start with our free health tools — symptom checkers, risk calculators, and a comprehensive metabolic health assessment. In 5 minutes, you'll have a clear picture of your metabolic, hormonal, and recovery risk factors.</p>
      <p>No account required, no payment, no sales pitch. Just data about your health.</p>
      <div class="expect-box">
        <h4>Available tools</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Metabolic Health Score Calculator</li>
          <li>Insulin Resistance Risk Assessment</li>
          <li>Hormone Symptom Checker</li>
          <li>Sleep Recovery Score</li>
          <li>Energy Optimization Assessment</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="process-step">
    <div class="step-header">
      <span class="step-badge">2</span>
      <h2>Understand What It Means</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="step-body">
      <p>Based on your results, we surface the most relevant guides, biomarker references, and explainers. Every piece of content is grounded in peer-reviewed research and explains not just the <em>what</em> but the <em>why</em>.</p>
      <p>Learn which biomarkers to pay attention to, what optimal ranges actually look like (not just "normal"), and what the current research says about your specific concerns.</p>
      <div class="expect-box">
        <h4>What you'll learn</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Which lab markers are most relevant to your symptoms</li>
          <li>The difference between "normal" and optimal reference ranges</li>
          <li>Root causes of common issues like fatigue, weight gain, and brain fog</li>
          <li>Evidence-based approaches backed by clinical research</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="process-step">
    <div class="step-header">
      <span class="step-badge">3</span>
      <h2>See What We Recommend</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="step-body">
      <p>Our medical advisory team reviews supplements, lab test kits, health devices, and other products — rating them on evidence quality, value, and who they're actually for.</p>
      <p>We're honest about what works and what doesn't. Every recommendation includes the research behind it, who it's best for, and when you might not need it.</p>
      <div class="expect-box">
        <h4>Recommendation categories</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>At-home lab test kits (hormone panels, metabolic panels, thyroid)</li>
          <li>Supplements with clinical trial backing</li>
          <li>Health monitoring devices (HRV, CGM, sleep trackers)</li>
          <li>Books and educational resources</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="process-step">
    <div class="step-header">
      <span class="step-badge">4</span>
      <h2>Talk to a Specialist (If You Need To)</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="step-body">
      <p>Sometimes you need a real doctor — for lab interpretation, hormone therapy, sleep studies, or complex cases. We maintain a vetted network of specialists in metabolic health, endocrinology, and sleep medicine.</p>
      <p>You tell us what you need. We match you with the right doctor. No marketplace, no browsing — we do the work of finding the right fit.</p>
      <div class="expect-box">
        <h4>Specialist areas</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Endocrinology (hormone imbalances, thyroid, testosterone)</li>
          <li>Metabolic medicine (insulin resistance, diabetes prevention)</li>
          <li>Sleep medicine (sleep apnea, chronic insomnia)</li>
          <li>Functional medicine (root-cause approaches)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bottom-cta">
  <h2>Start With the Free Assessment</h2>
  <p>The first step is understanding where you are. It takes 5 minutes, it's free, and you'll get instant results.</p>
  <a class="btn-primary" href="/assessment">Take the Assessment →</a>
</div>
{% endblock %}
